```dockerfile
# Stage 1: Build frontend with Node.js
FROM node:20-alpine AS frontend-builder

LABEL stage="frontend-builder"

WORKDIR /frontend

COPY frontend/package.json frontend/package-lock.json* frontend/yarn.lock* ./

RUN npm ci --only=production

COPY frontend/ .

RUN npm run build

# Stage 2: Build Python dependencies with Poetry
FROM python:3.12-slim AS python-builder

LABEL stage="python-builder"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq-dev \
    unixodbc-dev \
    build-essential && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

ENV PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1 \
    PYTHONDONTWRITEBYTECODE=1 \
    PIP_NO_CACHE_DIR=1 \
    PIP_DISABLE_PIP_VERSION_CHECK=1

RUN pip install poetry

COPY pyproject.toml poetry.lock ./

RUN poetry config virtualenvs.in-project true && \
    poetry install --no-interaction --no-ansi --only main

# Stage 3: Final runtime image
FROM python:3.12-slim

LABEL maintainer="Analytics Platform Team" \
      description="Python analytics platform with React frontend"

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    libpq5 \
    unixodbc \
    curl && \
    rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

RUN useradd -m -u 1000 superset

COPY --from=python-builder /app/.venv /app/.venv

COPY --from=frontend-builder /frontend/dist /app/frontend/dist

COPY . .

RUN chown -R superset:superset /app

USER superset

ENV PATH="/app/.venv/bin:$PATH" \
    PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1 \
    PYTHONDONTWRITEBYTECODE=1

EXPOSE 8088

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:8088/health || exit 1

CMD ["gunicorn", "-w", "4", "-b", "0.0.0.0:8088", "app:create_app()"]
